sequenceDiagram
    participant "Operator (SRE)" as OperatorSRE
    participant "Monitoring System" as MonitoringSystem
    participant "CI/CD System" as CICDSystem
    participant "Container Registry" as ContainerRegistry
    participant "Container Orchestrator" as ContainerOrchestrator
    participant "Application" as Application

    activate OperatorSRE
    MonitoringSystem->>OperatorSRE: 1. 1. Send Critical Alert: SLO Breach Detected (High Error Rate / Latency)
    OperatorSRE->>MonitoringSystem: 2. 2. Investigate Failure (Confirms new deployment is root cause)
    MonitoringSystem-->>OperatorSRE: Dashboard data confirms SLO breach correlates with deployment time.
    activate CICDSystem
    OperatorSRE->>CICDSystem: 3. 3. Trigger Rollback: 'Deploy Specific Version' Workflow
    CICDSystem-->>OperatorSRE: Workflow run started successfully.
    activate ContainerOrchestrator
    CICDSystem->>ContainerOrchestrator: 4. 4. Set New Image for Deployment
    ContainerOrchestrator-->>CICDSystem: Deployment 'product-service' image updated.
    ContainerOrchestrator->>ContainerRegistry: 5. 4a. Pull Image 'product-service:v1.2.0'
    ContainerRegistry-->>ContainerOrchestrator: Image layers downloaded.
    ContainerOrchestrator->>ContainerOrchestrator: 6. 4b. Execute Rolling Update Strategy
    CICDSystem->>OperatorSRE: 7. 5. Notify: Rollback Deployment Complete
    OperatorSRE->>Application: 8. 6. Validate: Check Health Endpoint
    Application-->>OperatorSRE: HTTP 200 OK, Status: Healthy
    OperatorSRE->>MonitoringSystem: 9. 7. Validate: Confirm Metrics Returned to Normal
    MonitoringSystem-->>OperatorSRE: Error rate and latency metrics are within SLO.

